---
title: Quick Comforting Bacon & Mushroom Boscaiola with Garlic Panini
description: When the craving for a creamy pasta dish hits there’s only one solution - a boscaiola! Soft and warming, it will fill up your belly with
love from the hearty mushrooms and bacon stirred through the sauce. Soak up the flavour with a side of classic garlic bread.
